data.text:
I had the great pleasure of meeting the new Medway Police Superintendant Tom Richards at Gun Wharf this morning.

In my capacity as Lead Member for Children’s Services I had the opportunity of discussing Young People with Tom and look forward very much to working with him in the future.

Medway Council has always been extremely fortunate in having a very close professional relationship with Kent Police Medway and I am confident that that relationship can only get stronger in the future.

Tags: gun wharf, Kent Police Medway, medway council, professional relationship, Tom, Tom Richards
